FBIS3-11633 "drlat057_o_94007" FBIS-LAT-94-057 Document Type:Daily Report 24 Mar 1994 Colombia Presidential Election Postponed Until 29 May PA2403005494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 in Spanish 0000 GMT 24 Mar 94 PA2403005494 Santa Fe de Bogota Inravision Television Cadena 1 Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [From the "24 Hours" newscast] [Text] Attention: The Constitutional Court changed part of the Electoral Law this evening, 23 March. This organization changed the date for the presidential and vice presidential election from 8 May to 29 May. Should there be a runoff election -- that is, between the two candidates who garner the most votes -- the definitive election of President Cesar Gaviria's successor will be on 19 June. Other articles of the Electoral Law were also changed.
